Texas / w Okla cattle steady in light test - USDA . Trade slow in the panhandle area early Wednesday . Slaughter steers and heifers steady in a light test . Feedlots reporting moderate inquiry from buyers . Sales reported on 3 , 100 head slaughter steers and 1 , 100 heifers ; 45 , 700 head confirmed for the week to date which includes 22 , 400 formulated and 2 , 800 head previously contracted cattle to be shipped this week . Slaughter Steers Select and Choice 2 - 3 1100 - 1250 lbs 65 . 00 . Pen Select , few Choice 2 - 3 1150 lbs 64 . 50 . Slaughter Heifers Select and Choice 2 - 3 1000 - 1150 lbs 65 . 00 . ( ( Chicago newsdesk 312 - 408 - 8720 ) ) 
